stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RESET

    RESET --> INIT: mc_rstn deasserted
    INIT --> ACTIVE: init_done
    INIT --> INIT_ERROR: init_error

    ACTIVE --> ACTIVE_PD: req_low_power + banks open
    ACTIVE --> PRECHARGE_PD: req_low_power + banks idle
    ACTIVE --> SELF_REFRESH: req_self_refresh (DDR2 or LPDDR2)
    ACTIVE --> DPD: req_dpd (LPDDR2 only)

    ACTIVE_PD --> ACTIVE: req_active
    PRECHARGE_PD --> ACTIVE: req_active

    SELF_REFRESH --> ACTIVE: req_active + tXSNR elapsed

    DPD --> INIT: req_active (full re-init required)

    INIT_ERROR --> INIT: soft_reset via CSR

    note right of SELF_REFRESH
      CKE low
      DRAM self-refreshes
      Controller tREFI paused
    end note

    note right of DPD
      LPDDR2 only
      DRAM content lost
      SoC must flush caches first
    end note

    note left of INIT
      Microprogram engine
      executes memtype-specific
      step table
    end note
